		<div class="topic">
		[SOLVED] NO SOUND (Arch linux)	</div>
	<div class="content">
		Hi all,<br><br>Steam has always worked perfectly fine on my Arch box. However, after having not run steam for a couple months, I am suddenly getting NO SOUND at all from any Steam games. Any ideas?<br><br>Arch Linux<br>steam 1.0.0.54-1<br><br>Thanks,<br>Azalus<br><br>EDIT: Fixed it by choosing the correct sound card in Pavucontrol	</div>
